     function stringGen(len) {
      var text = "";
      var charset = "abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789";
      for( var i=0; i < len; i++ )
      text += charset.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random() * charset.length));
      return text;
     }
     function createCookie(name, value, days) {
         var expires;
         if (days) {
             var date = new Date();
             date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
             expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
         } else {
             expires = "";
         }
         document.cookie = encodeURIComponent(name) + "=" + encodeURIComponent(value) + expires + "; domain=.walgreens.com; path=/"+ "; secure:''";
     }
     function readCookie(name) {
      var nameEQ = encodeURIComponent(name) + "=";
      var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
      for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
      var c = ca[i];
      while (c.charAt(0) === ' ') c = c.substring(1, c.length);
      if (c.indexOf(nameEQ) === 0) return decodeURIComponent(c.substring(nameEQ.length, c.length));
      }
      return null;
     }
     function eraseCookie(name) {
      createCookie(name, "", -1);
     }
     var cookieList = document.cookie.split(';');
     var cookienames = []; 
     for(var i=0; i<cookieList.length ; i++){
         cookienames.push(cookieList[i].split('=')[0].trim());
     };
     if (cookienames.indexOf("wag_sid") < 0) {
      var rand = stringGen(24);
      createCookie("wag_sid",rand);
     }

<script type="text/javascript">
function callTypedDtm(){
$('#ntt-placeholder').val($('#ntt-placeholder').val().replace(/;/g, ' ').replace(/`/g, ''));
sessionStorage.removeItem('searchOffset');
sessionStorage.removeItem('itemsToLoad');
$(document).trigger("triggerDTM", "BAS-Search-Typed-Evar96-Tracking");
}
function typehead(){
if(typeof typeAheadGetData !== 'undefined'){
if(document.readyState === "complete"){
typeAheadGetData();
} else {
$(window).load(function(){
typeAheadGetData();
});
}
}
$('.wag-search-clr-close-icon').on("click",function(e){
$(this).hide();
$('#ntt-placeholder').val('');
$('#ntt-placeholder').focus();
$('.wag-search-clr-close-icon').hide();
});
$('#wag-typeaheadcontainer').hide();
$('.over-flow-hidden').removeClass('over-flow-hidden');
var isMobiledevice = (typeof window.matchMedia !== 'undefined')?(window.matchMedia("(max-width: 767px)").matches):($(window).width() <= 767);
if (isMobiledevice) {   
$(".wag-mobile-search-area").on("focus","#ntt-placeholder",function(){
if($("#ntt-placeholder").val().length > 0){ 
$('.wag-search-clr-close-icon').show();
}else{ 
$('.wag-search-clr-close-icon').hide();
}    
});
}
$(document).mouseup(function (e){
var container = $("#wag-typeaheadcontainer");
var searchIcon=$('.icon-Search');
if (!container.is(e.target) && container.has(e.target).length === 0 && !searchIcon.is(e.target))
{
container.hide();
$('#wag-typeaheadlists').empty();
}
});
$('#header-search').on("click",function(e){
sessionStorage.setItem("navHeaderSearchBoxFlag",true);
});
if ( window.location.href.indexOf("results.jsp?") > 0 ) {
$("#ntt-placeholder").val($("#keyword").val());
}
$(window).load(function(){
setTimeout(function() {
if($('#wag-typeaheadcontainer').is(':visible') && navigator.appVersion.indexOf("MSIE") != -1) {
$('#wag-typeaheadcontainer').hide();
$('.over-flow-hidden').removeClass('over-flow-hidden');
}
},1000);
});
}
function typeheadDocReady(){
$.support.placeholder = ('placeholder' in document.createElement('input'));
var changeSearchBoxPlaceholder = function () {
var searchBox = $('input[id=ntt-placeholder]');
var isDesktop=!(/iPad|iPhone|iPod|android/i.test(navigator.platform));
if( $(window).width() >= 768 && $(window).width() <= 1024) {
if(isDesktop){
$("#wag-type-right-product-list").removeClass('hidden-sm hidden-md');
$("#wag-typeaheadlists").removeClass('wag-typeahead-list-full-width');
}else{
$("#wag-typeaheadlists").addClass('wag-typeahead-list-full-width');
}
searchBox.attr('placeholder',"Search");
} else {
searchBox.attr('placeholder',"Search by keyword or item #");
}
if (!$.support.placeholder) {
searchBox.focus(function () {
if ($(this).val() == $(this).attr("placeholder")) $(this).val("");
}).blur(function () {
if ($(this).val() == "") $(this).val($(this).attr("placeholder"));
}).blur();
$("[placeholder]").parents("form").submit(function () {
$(this).find('[placeholder]').each(function() {
if ($(this).val() == $(this).attr("placeholder")) {
$(this).val("");
}
});
});
}
};
$(window).resize( changeSearchBoxPlaceholder );
}
if (typeof $ !== 'undefined') {
$(document).ready(function(){
if(typeof getPastSearchResult !== 'undefined'){getPastSearchResult();}
typeheadDocReady();
typehead();
});
}
</script>
